history.content:
Hi, I have a few questions:

1. Is there a form or action I need to take to formally withdraw/not attend Spring 2021?

2. I received an email today saying that if I don't enroll in any classes for Spring 2021, my CalNet account will enter a 274 day grace period after Fall 2020 ends. How do I clear any holds I might have on my CalCentral account for readmission purposes if I can't access CalCentral?

3. When should I hear back if my readmission application was approved or not?

Thanks in advance!
history.subject: Readmission Questions - L&S
